# Generated by aws/build.mjs — copies of ../api, ../knowledge,
# ../email-templates plus the zip artifacts. Regenerate with
# `node aws/build.mjs` rather than committing these; keeps the Lambda
# packages from silently drifting out of sync with the real source.
